              [BRANCH:1a1a1:需要]
                [STEP:1a1a1.1] @客戶 {specs/ui/上傳身分文件.md}
              [BRANCH:1a1a1:免除]
                [STEP:1a1a1.2] @風控小組 {specs/commands/直接放行高額交易.feature}
              [BRANCH:1a1a1:else]
                [STEP:1a1a1.3] @風控小組 {specs/commands/轉人工專案處理.feature}
            [MERGE:1a1a1]
          [BRANCH:1a1a:小額]
            [STEP:1a1a.2] @風控小組 {specs/commands/自動放行小額交易.feature}
        [MERGE:1a1a]
      [BRANCH:1a1:駁回]
        [STEP:1a1.2] @風控小組 {specs/commands/紀錄拒絕原因.feature}
        [STEP:1a1.3] @通知系統 {specs/commands/通知客戶交易拒絕.feature}
        [FINAL]
      [BRANCH:1a1:改用超商 -> 1a.2]
    [MERGE:1a1]
  [BRANCH:1a:超商]
    [STEP:1a.2] @客戶 {specs/ui/選取超商門市.md}
    [DECISION:1a2] 超商門市是否可用
      [BRANCH:1a2:可用]
        [STEP:1a2.1] @通知系統 {specs/commands/寄送超商付款碼.feature}
      [BRANCH:1a2:店家停業改信用卡 -> 1a.1]
    [MERGE:1a2]
  [BRANCH:1a:else]
    [STEP:1a.3] @通知系統 {specs/ui/顯示無支援付款方式.md}
[MERGE:1a]

